item.title: Imperial rugby down RUM(s)
item.author: Felix Editor,David Nielson-Scot,
item.description: Still buzzing after their triumph last week, Imperial were roaring to get at a UCL Medical School (RUMS) side which had evaded defeat in the past five meetings, including a 49-10 drubbing earlier this season.
